  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Addameer - Irish Aid Core Funding 2020</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promotion and protection of human rights is a core principle in Ireland&#x2019;s development policy. Under the Human Rights and Democratisation Scheme, Ireland has key funding relationships with Israeli and Palestinian NGOs which monitor human rights violations and promote greater accountability by both the Israeli and Palestinian authorities. Addameer is the leading Palestinian prisoners&#x2019; rights association. The organisation assists prisoners and their families through the provision of free legal advice and representation in Israeli military courts, seeking to guarantee minimum rights where possible and, where not, raising awareness and lobbying for change in practices.</narrative>
  </description>
